qNL: How many departments are led by heads who are not mentioned?
true_SQL: SELECT count(*) FROM department WHERE department_id NOT IN (SELECT department_id FROM management);
qSQL: SELECT COUNT(*)  FROM department  WHERE Department_ID NOT IN (SELECT Department_ID FROM management);

qNL: List the states where both the secretary of 'Treasury' department and the secretary of 'Homeland Security' were born.
true_SQL: SELECT T3.born_state FROM department AS T1 JOIN management AS T2 ON T1.department_id  =  T2.department_id JOIN head AS T3 ON T2.head_id  =  T3.head_id WHERE T1.name  =  'Treasury' INTERSECT SELECT T3.born_state FROM department AS T1 JOIN management AS T2 ON T1.department_id  =  T2.department_id JOIN head AS T3 ON T2.head_id  =  T3.head_id WHERE T1.name  =  'Homeland Security'
qSQL: SELECT h1.born_state FROM head AS h1 JOIN management AS m1 ON h1.head_ID = m1.head_ID JOIN department AS d1 ON m1.Department_ID = d1.Department_ID WHERE d1.Name = 'Treasury' INTERSECT SELECT h2.born_state FROM head AS h2 JOIN management AS m2 ON h2.head_ID = m2.head_ID JOIN department AS d2 ON m2.Department_ID = d2.Department_ID WHERE d2.Name = 'Homeland Security';

qNL: Which department has more than 1 head at a time? List the id, name and the number of heads.
true_SQL: SELECT T1.department_id ,  T1.name ,  count(*) FROM management AS T2 JOIN department AS T1 ON T1.department_id  =  T2.department_id GROUP BY T1.department_id HAVING count(*)  >  1
qSQL: SELECT department.Department_ID, department.Name, COUNT(management.head_ID) as Number_of_Heads FROM department JOIN management ON department.Department_ID = management.Department_ID GROUP BY department.Department_ID, department.Name HAVING COUNT(management.head_ID) > 1;
